video.title: Let's Stream GTA IV Live w/ Jesus - Feb. 26th, 2013 Recording FAIL
video.description:
Let's Stream GTA IV Live w/ Jesus - Feb. 26th, 2013 Recording FAIL
That's what happens in a day that everything goes wrong. It started at 5:03 PM Eastern Time due to technical difficulties, and it lasted only 25:31. It  only lasted 25:31 due to a power outage, and the power outage lasted 3 HOURS!
